{"tid":1811140,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新任中聯辦主任 前年訪港時曾與林鄭月娥會面","createTime":"2020-01-04T12:08:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T12:32:01.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"05c4b55705fa524f2820e78e39e18b90741c7ee4","tid":1811140,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:08:56.000Z","msg":"全國人大財政經濟委員會副主任委員駱惠寧接任中聯辦主任。現年65歲的駱惠寧前年擔任山西省委書記時到訪本港，當時到禮賓府與特首林鄭月娥會面。<br />\n<br />\n駱惠寧曾經主政青海及山西，從政經歷中未有涉足港澳事務，但曾經與兩位現任政治局常委汪洋及趙樂際共事。駱惠寧1999年擔任安徽省委常委及宣傳部部長，當時汪洋為安徽省副省長。<br />\n<br />\n駱惠寧2003年調往青海出任省委副書記，當時趙樂際就先後出任青海省省長及省委書記。駱惠寧早於2012年的十八大，已經晉身成為中央委員，2017年的十九大連任中央委員。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501023-20200104.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501023-20200104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=2525475c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501023-20200104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e58505e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501023-20200104.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"20f3f7b70559a71e29ca035a34cea599839f1bb7","tid":1811140,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:11:45.000Z","msg":"推到比立場/蘋果/議員睇到<br />\n［停止使用建制稱呼親共人士］<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZQscQho.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZQscQho.jpg&h=56da94ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n強烈要求使用「共派」取代「建制」稱呼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1811104\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1811104</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6c6ac464bed78b286821ffdb2a3ddc26778bda04","tid":1811140,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:12:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5bcba83c